{
  "id": 80,
  "nameSimple": "'Abasa",
  "nameArabic": "عبس",
  "versesCount": 42,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5759,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "80:1",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101803,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He [i.e., the Prophet (ﷺ) ] frowned and turned away",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752472,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他曾皱眉，而且转身离去，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5760,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "80:2",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلْأَعْمَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101814,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Because there came to him the blind man,<sup foot_note=230323>1</sup> [interrupting].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752473,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "因为那个盲人来到他的面前。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5761,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "80:3",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101825,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But what would make you perceive, [O Muḥammad], that perhaps he might be purified<sup foot_note=230324>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752474,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你怎能知道呢？他也许能受熏陶，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5762,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "80:4",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰٓ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101836,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752475,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "或听忠告，而蒙教益。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5763,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "80:5",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسْتَغْنَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101840,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "As for he who thinks himself without need,<sup foot_note=230325>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752476,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "至于自满者，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5764,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "80:6",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101841,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "To him you give attention.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752477,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你都逢迎他，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5765,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "80:7",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101842,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified.<sup foot_note=230326>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752478,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他不受熏陶，于你何干？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5766,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "80:8",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101843,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752479,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "至于殷勤地来请教你，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5767,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "80:9",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101844,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "While he fears [Allāh],",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752480,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "而且心怀敬畏者，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5768,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "80:10",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101804,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "From him you are distracted.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752481,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你却怠慢他。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5769,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "80:11",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101805,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "No! Indeed, they [i.e., these verses] are a reminder;",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752482,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "绝不然！这确是一种教训。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5770,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "80:12",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101806,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So whoever wills may remember it.<sup foot_note=230329>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752483,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "谁欲诵读它，就叫谁诵读它吧",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5771,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "80:13",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فِى صُحُفٍ مُّكَرَّمَةٍ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101807,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[It is recorded] in honored sheets,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752484,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "它在珍贵的册页里；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5772,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "80:14",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّرْفُوعَةٍ مُّطَهَّرَةٍۭ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101808,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Exalted and purified,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752485,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那些册页，是被称扬的，是被涤净的，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5773,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "80:15",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "بِأَيْدِى سَفَرَةٍ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101809,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752486,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "是在许多书记的手里的；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5774,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "80:16",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كِرَامٍۭ بَرَرَةٍ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101810,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Noble and dutiful.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752487,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那些书记，是尊贵的，是善良的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5775,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "80:17",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قُتِلَ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مَآ أَكْفَرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101811,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Destroyed [i.e., cursed] is man;<sup foot_note=230332>1</sup> how disbelieving is he.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752488,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "该死的人！他是何等的忘恩！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5776,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "80:18",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101812,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "From what thing [i.e., substance] did He create him?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752489,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "安拉曾用什么创造他的呢？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5777,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "80:19",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101813,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him;<sup foot_note=230333>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752490,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "是用精液。他曾创造他，并预定他发育的程序。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5778,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "verseKey": "80:20",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101815,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then He eased the way for him;<sup foot_note=230334>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752491,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，他使他的道路平易。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5779,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "verseKey": "80:21",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقْبَرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101816,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him.<sup foot_note=230335>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752492,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，他使他死，并安葬他。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5780,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "verseKey": "80:22",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101817,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then when He wills, He will resurrect him.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752493,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，当他意欲的时候，他使他复活。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5781,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "verseKey": "80:23",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101818,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "No! He [i.e., man] has not yet accomplished what He commanded him.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752494,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "绝不然，他还没有奉行他所命令他的事务。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5782,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "verseKey": "80:24",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَلْيَنظُرِ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101819,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then let mankind look at his food -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752495,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "教人观察自己的食物吧！",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5783,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "verseKey": "80:25",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا ٱلْمَآءَ صَبًّا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101820,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "How We poured down water in torrents,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752496,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我将雨水大量地倾注下来。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5784,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "verseKey": "80:26",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا ٱلْأَرْضَ شَقًّا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101821,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts],",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752497,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，我使地面奇异地裂开，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5785,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "verseKey": "80:27",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَأَنۢبَتْنَا فِيهَا حَبًّا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101822,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And caused to grow within it grain",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752498,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我在大地上生产百谷，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5786,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "verseKey": "80:28",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَعِنَبًا وَقَضْبًا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101823,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And grapes and herbage",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752499,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "与葡萄和苜蓿，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5787,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "verseKey": "80:29",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَزَيْتُونًا وَنَخْلًا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101824,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And olive and palm trees",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752500,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "与橄榄和海枣，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5788,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "verseKey": "80:30",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلْبًا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101826,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And gardens of dense shrubbery",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752501,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "与茂密的园圃，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5789,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "verseKey": "80:31",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَفَـٰكِهَةً وَأَبًّا",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101827,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And fruit and grass -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752502,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "水果和牧草，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5790,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "verseKey": "80:32",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مَّتَـٰعًا لَّكُمْ وَلِأَنْعَـٰمِكُمْ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101828,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[As] enjoyment [i.e., provision] for you and your grazing livestock.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752503,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以供你们和你们的牲畜享受。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5791,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "verseKey": "80:33",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101829,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But when there comes the Deafening Blast<sup foot_note=230338>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752504,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当震耳欲聋的轰声来临的时候，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5792,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "verseKey": "80:34",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101830,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "On the Day a man will flee from his brother",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752505,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，各人将逃避自己的弟兄、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5793,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "verseKey": "80:35",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101831,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And his mother and his father",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752506,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "自己的父母、",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5794,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "verseKey": "80:36",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَصَـٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101832,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And his wife and his children,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752507,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "自己的妻子儿女；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5795,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "verseKey": "80:37",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "لِكُلِّ ٱمْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101833,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "For every man, that Day, will be a matter adequate for him.<sup foot_note=230339>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752508,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，各人将自顾不暇；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5796,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "verseKey": "80:38",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُّسْفِرَةٌ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101834,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Some] faces, that Day, will be bright -",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752509,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，许多面目是光华的，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5797,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "verseKey": "80:39",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ضَاحِكَةٌ مُّسْتَبْشِرَةٌ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101835,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Laughing, rejoicing at good news.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752510,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "是喜笑的，是愉快的；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5798,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "verseKey": "80:40",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْهَا غَبَرَةٌ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101837,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [other] faces, that Day, will have upon them dust.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752511,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "在那日，许多面目上，将有灰尘，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5799,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "verseKey": "80:41",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "تَرْهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101838,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Blackness will cover them.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752512,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "黧黑将蒙蔽它。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5800,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "verseKey": "80:42",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 234,
      "rukuNumber": 524,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْكَفَرَةُ ٱلْفَجَرَةُ",
      "pageNumber": 585,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101839,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Those are the disbelievers, the wicked ones.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752513,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这等人，是不信道的，是荒淫的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}